{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-099","title":"在夜市","sectionId":"chapter-04","sectionTitle":"商店购物买买买","pageStart":498,"pageEnd":502,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":31,"duplicateEntryCount":4,"pages":[{"number":498,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"99 在夜市"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"night market 夜市","headword":"night market"},{"type":"entry","text":"night fair 夜市","headword":"night fair"},{"type":"entry","text":"food stand 小吃摊","headword":"food stand"},{"type":"entry","text":"special snack 特色小吃","headword":"special snack"},{"type":"entry","text":"street vendor 摊贩","headword":"street vendor"},{"type":"entry","text":"shopkeeper [ˈʃɒpkiːpə(r)]","headword":"shopkeeper"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.店主"},{"type":"entry","text":"barbecue [ˈbɑːbɪkjuː]","headword":"barbecue"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.烧烤"},{"type":"note","text":"◎barbecue sauce烤肉酱/Mongolian barbecue蒙古烤肉/Korean barbecue"},{"type":"text","text":"韩国烤肉"},{"type":"entry","text":"shish kebab 烤肉串","headword":"shish kebab"},{"type":"entry","text":"Chinese hamburger 肉夹馍","headword":"Chinese hamburger"},{"type":"entry","text":"Wuhan dry noodles 武汉热干面","headword":"Wuhan dry noodles"},{"type":"entry","text":"stinky tofu 臭豆腐","headword":"stinky tofu"}]},{"number":499,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"draft beer 生啤；扎啤","headword":"draft beer"},{"type":"entry","text":"fresh juice 鲜榨果汁","headword":"fresh juice"},{"type":"entry","text":"ring toss game 抛圈游戏","headword":"ring toss game"},{"type":"entry","text":"pinball [ˈpɪnbɔːl]","headword":"pinball"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.弹球"},{"type":"note","text":"◎pinball machine弹珠机"},{"type":"entry","text":"fishing [ˈfɪʃɪŋ]","headword":"fishing"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.钓鱼"},{"type":"note","text":"◎go fishing去钓鱼"},{"type":"entry","text":"doll machine 夹娃娃机","headword":"doll machine"},{"type":"entry","text":"capsule toy machine 扭蛋机","headword":"capsule toy machine"},{"type":"entry","text":"light bulb 电灯泡","headword":"light bulb"},{"type":"entry","text":"appointment [əˈpɔɪntmənt]","headword":"appointment"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.约会"},{"type":"note","text":"◎making an appointment预约"},{"type":"entry","text":"relaxed [rɪˈlækst]","headword":"relaxed"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.轻松的"},{"type":"entry","text":"disordered [dɪsˈɔːdəd]","headword":"disordered"}]},{"number":500,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"a.混乱的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎disordered state无序状态"},{"type":"entry","text":"crowd [kraʊd]","headword":"crowd"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.人群"},{"type":"entry","text":"hungry [ˈhʌŋɡri]","headword":"hungry"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.饥饿的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎be hungry for渴望/hungry ghost饿鬼"},{"type":"entry","text":"beggar [ˈbeɡə(r)]","headword":"beggar"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.乞丐"},{"type":"note","text":"◎beggars can't be choosers饥不择食"},{"type":"entry","text":"drunkard [ˈdrʌŋkəd]","headword":"drunkard"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.醉鬼"},{"type":"entry","text":"police [pəˈliːs]","headword":"police"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.警察"},{"type":"note","text":"◎police office警察局"},{"type":"entry","text":"urban management officer 城管","headword":"urban management officer"}]},{"number":501,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"street artist 街头艺人","headword":"street artist"},{"type":"entry","text":"rubbish [ˈrʌbɪʃ]","headword":"rubbish"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.垃圾"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"entry","text":"Night markets in Taiwan台湾夜市","headword":"Night markets in Taiwan"},{"type":"text","text":"Taiwan has long been known for its night markets. According to the"},{"type":"text","text":"island's tourism bureau, night markets attract more than 70% of foreign"},{"type":"text","text":"visitors. The popularity of these nightly bazaars even prompted the bureau"},{"type":"text","text":"to come up with an app in which players can be virtual street hawkers in the"},{"type":"text","text":"markets. But as Taiwan becomes more globalised, so does the selection at"},{"type":"text","text":"the night markets. Visitors to Taipei's famed Raohe Night Market can still"},{"type":"text","text":"get their fill of Taiwanese standbys like stinky tofu, pork intestine soup and"},{"type":"text","text":"pig's blood rice cakes smothered with peanut powder. But those in the mood"},{"type":"text","text":"for something a little different can now also find Italian pizza cones, French"},{"type":"text","text":"crepes and Thai banana roti."},{"type":"text","text":"台湾夜市一直以来都是闻名中外。据台湾旅游局透露，台湾夜市"},{"type":"text","text":"吸引了70%以上的国外游客。这些夜市的人气高涨，也促使旅游局推"},{"type":"text","text":"出了一款应用，这款应用可以使用户成为这些市场的虚拟摊贩。但随"},{"type":"text","text":"着台湾变得更加全球化，夜市提供的选择也更具国际特色。在台北有"},{"type":"text","text":"名的饶河街夜市，游客仍然可以吃到传统的台湾美食，如臭豆腐、猪"},{"type":"text","text":"肠汤、铺着花生碎的猪血糕。但对于那些想吃点不同风味美食的游客"},{"type":"text","text":"来说，现在还可以吃到意大利手握比萨、法式可丽饼和泰式香蕉煎"},{"type":"text","text":"饼。"}]},{"number":502,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"Chapter5 健康养生最重要"}]}]}